:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdcXAffF1AiuilQywQy3E-NwlP4H5aNHZgo8Pg7_iBRS&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-Generation-Cancelling-Transparency-Personalized%2Fdp%2FB0BDHWDR12">AirPods Pro</a>的音质更饱满、功能更丰富，而且与 Apple 一样友好。它们目前以 200 美元的价格出售，这是我们最近几个月经常看到的另一笔交易，但仍然比 Apple 的标价低 50 美元。 AirPods Pro 是我们 <a data-i13n="cpos:94;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-wireless-earbuds-120058222.html">最佳无线耳塞</a>指南中的“iOS 最佳选择”。</p><h2> Roku、谷歌和亚马逊 4K 流媒体棒</h2><p><core-commerce id="274ba55cf8e84447a29ec793da483257" data-type="product-list"></p><p>现在是进入市场购买新的 4K 流媒体棒的好时机。 <a data-i13n="cpos:95;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9Sb2t1LVN0cmVhbWluZy1EZXZpY2UtVmlzaW9uLUNvbnRyb2xzL2RwL0IwOUJLQ0RYWkM_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMTJoLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIwNmZmYmZkOS01MzBkLTRlZmMtODk3Mi0yMmZhYzVjZTVmOWMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAbL6cZwwniC6SwRQrVXjpDySEYW90r0Ilvm1nhNtK3iT&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FRoku-Streaming-Device-Vision-Controls%2Fdp%2FB09BKCDXZC">Roku Streaming Stick 4K</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:96;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbH0p3CHmOnNRML50nkv76uGUsPAfm6f9gwUUSK6iHT_&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FChromecast-Google-TV-Streaming-Entertainment%2Fdp